{"tid":2430462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：疫苗接種計劃不會因為今次個案而暫停　除非多人出現大量不尋常副作用","createTime":"2021-03-03T03:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T06:39:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":24,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"4a61615f361af5904e4b18fdbb1fc18e0cf07d5b","tid":2430462,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"他承認今次事件可能影響市民接種疫苗的信心，但疫苗接種計劃不會因為今次個案而暫停，除非多人打針後出現吉巴氏症、全身無力等大量不尋常副作用情況才要暫停。<br />\n<br />\n許續指，感染武肺病毒對慢性病患者的風險較接種疫苗更大，因為疫苗不會導致炎症，並引述挪威早前有30多位長者接種疫苗後死亡，世衛亦認為與疫苗無關，強調長期病患者如果本身將病情控制得好，是絕對適宜接種疫苗，呼籲有疑惑的慢性病患者，應該向家庭醫生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381318\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381318&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=2db03f7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381318</a>"},{"pid":"0b2954ae4af7a23a670fc12f599ad886c06759bc","tid":2430462,"uid":93600,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"咁你打咗科興未？"},{"pid":"6a0a7e0e86f1ba1db30575cde262f00f1ce67c06","tid":2430462,"uid":156659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"又繼續派彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69fe895d022e01abc8bf3c7b80a3df4e1af4969","tid":2430462,"uid":361247,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"所以預言家話全球一半人口,我估疫苗會殺年過50過批人"},{"pid":"38ad8607fb27bf5a2a64e2717d778bdcb845fd00","tid":2430462,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"而家停，尾款咪落唔到袋，先無咁傻"},{"pid":"08f5662ed725845b548daf440b2b29d7e45421a4","tid":2430462,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"人渣 醫畜"},{"pid":"4d846342d039f373a2ddc25fe84af3042eca6387","tid":2430462,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cited